data.meta_description: Nicolas Prevost was born on January 14, 1601 in St Denis, Paris, Ile-De-France, France, son of Pierre Prevost and Charlotte Vie. He died on August 10, 1653 in Bobigny, Paris, Ile-De-France, France. This information is part of Km&be by KM on Genealogy Online.
